imdb.plot outline: We follow Rosie, a dope slinging heart breaker as she navigates a volatile, tumultuous relationship with her pot head boyfriend, Willy. Wetmouth, her Soundcloud rapper older brother has a secret plan to keep them together. In a scare with the police, Wetmouth goes into a kush coma and Willy and Rosie must go into his psyche to help him escape. But will they be able to find the way out?
